Crafting Expertise	KEY:Machinesmith ~ Crafting Expertise	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:MachinesmithClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Supernatural					DEFINE:MachinesmithCraftingExpertiseLVL|0												DESC:At 3rd level, the machinesmith gains Craft Wondrous Item as a bonus feat.|PREVARGTEQ:MachinesmithCraftingExpertiseLVL,3	DESC:At 8th level he gains Craft Magic Arms and Armor.|PREVARGTEQ:MachinesmithCraftingExpertiseLVL,8	DESC:At 15th level he gains the Craft Construct feat.|PREVARGTEQ:MachinesmithCraftingExpertiseLVL,15	DESC:He uses his machinesmith levels in place of caster level when making such items. In order to add a special ability to an item, he must have access to the prerequisite spells, either through use of a magical item or cast by another spellcaster.	AUTO:FEAT|Craft Wondrous Item|PREVARGTEQ:MachinesmithCraftingExpertiseLVL,3	AUTO:FEAT|Craft Magic Arms and Armor|PREVARGTEQ:MachinesmithCraftingExpertiseLVL,8	AUTO:FEAT|Craft Construct|PREVARGTEQ:MachinesmithCraftingExpertiseLVL,15	SOURCEPAGE:p.10
Axiom				KEY:Machinesmith ~ Axiom			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:MachinesmithClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Supernatural																							DESC:Beginning at 7th level, the machinesmith develops an innate ability to ground magic with science. The machinesmith can "lose" any prepared prototype of 3rd level or higher in order to have it function as a Dispel Magic spell of a caster level equal to their machinesmith level. SOURCEPAGE:p.10

