Combat Engineer	KEY:Machinesmith Archetype ~ Combat Engineer	CATEGORY:Archetype	TYPE:Archetype.MachinesmithArchetype.MachinesmithWeaponProficiencies.MachinesmithCrafter.MachinesmithCraftingExpertise	PRECLASS:1,Machinesmith=1	PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Archetype,Machinesmith Archetype ~ Combat Engineer],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Archetype,TYPE=MachinesmithWeaponProficiencies,TYPE=MachinesmithCrafter]	DESC:On the frontlines, machinesmiths often don't have the luxury of time to deploy fanciful strategies or build complex devices. More often than not, the stresses of combat demand that they take a pragmatic approach; building for durability, learning to use needed equipment on the fly, and ready to use strength of arms when necessary. These machinesmiths are known as combat engineers.	ABILITY:Machinesmith Class Feature|AUTOMATIC|Combat Engineer ~ Weapon and Armor Proficiencies|PRECLASS:1,Machinesmith=1	ABILITY:Machinesmith Class Feature|AUTOMATIC|Combat Engineer ~ Diminished Prototypes|PRECLASS:1,Machinesmith=1	ABILITY:Machinesmith Class Feature|AUTOMATIC|Combat Engineer ~ Combat Awareness|PRECLASS:1,Machinesmith=1	ABILITY:Machinesmith Class Feature|AUTOMATIC|Combat Engineer ~ Rough and Ready|PRECLASS:1,Machinesmith=3	COST:0	SOURCEPAGE:p.13	ASPECT:Archetype Base Class|Machinesmith

